Additional coverage: &lt;a href="https://www.unite.ai/claudes-skills-framework-quietly-becomes-an-industry-standard/"&gt;Unite.AI&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://simonw.substack.com/p/openai-are-quietly-adopting-skills"&gt;Simon W. newsletter&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://venturebeat.com/ai/anthropic-launches-enterprise-agent-skills-and-opens-the-standard"&gt;VentureBeat&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://www.perplexity.ai/page/openai-adopts-anthropic-s-modu-KHRvdqZOQqC2hhKhflFhCw"&gt;Perplexity&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://the-decoder.com/openai-quietly-adopts-anthropics-modular-skills-framework-to-boost-agent-capabilities/"&gt;The Decoder&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://infotech.report/top-stories/openaianthropicskills"&gt;InfoTech.Report&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://jessleao.substack.com/p/google-wont-stop-shipping"&gt;Jess Leão&lt;/a&gt;
